    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required Gradation levels at MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per the ASME V&V 40 requirements matrix for a Class II device with Medium model influence and High decision consequence. The model form factor was evaluated through a rigorous qualitative expert review process that provided high confidence in model adequacy. The overall evidence base supports acceptance of the CFD hemolysis prediction model for the CPB COU at the stated risk level.",
